title: Detective School Dropouts (TV/VCRrip) (SteRipper)
description:
In honor and celebration of the 10th anniversary of The Pirate Bay, I share with all of you a movie I've been working on for the last month or so.

Detective School Dropouts was a film that got overlooked greatly in theaters, and for some it became one of those films you can enjoy now, but just can't seem to find anywhere.

It's a TV/VCR rip. I recorded it from TV to my VCR years ago, and then copied it to MP4 in July.

I took awhile to clean up (Audio and Video quality was shit), but It looks and sounds good.

Happy Anniversary to The Pirate Bay!
Don't run out of duct tape.

--SteRipper
